1. Dinner at Le Bordeaux, @intercontinental_bordeaux 
2. Place du Parlement
3. La Grosse Cloche
4. The most famous local dessert, the Canelé
5. Sauternes room of @intercontinental_bordeaux 
6. Sunrise view of the Opera House
7. Place de la Bourse
8. Porte Cailhau
